### Quick status

- **Do first, non-negotiable:** §1 — add the `.gitignore` before a real `.env` ever exists. This is the single highest-stakes housekeeping item across all your repos, because the secret here is a wallet key on a public repo.
- **The credibility decision:** §2 — testnet vs. persistent chain determines whether this delivers the permanence the paper claims or only demonstrates it.
- **Optional growth:** §3 — the three paper-named extensions, built when the framework needs to scale.
